---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <main>
    <section id="hero" class="pt-40">
      <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-12">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-heading font-light mb-8">
          IQ World Terms & Conditions
        </h1>
        <p
          class="text-base md:text-lg max-w-xl mb-24 font-normal font-heading uppercase text-black/80"
        >
          TERMS AND CONDITIONS FOR IQ WORLD APPLICATION AND SERVICES
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="tnc-content" class="pb-10 pt-20 max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">IQ World — Terms & Conditions and Privacy Policy</h2>
        
        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-6 mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-800">Agreement</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-700">
            By using IQ WORLD's application or website, you agree to all the terms and conditions outlined here. 
            If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you should not use the application or website.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Preamble</h3>
        <p class="mb-6">
          IQ WORLD values your privacy and is committed to protecting it. This Privacy Policy outlines how 
          IQ WORLD collects, uses, and discloses information provided by users and customers. The policy may 
          be updated from time to time.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg mb-6">
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Definitions:</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm">
            <li>• <strong>Platform:</strong> IQ WORLD's software portal and website</li>
            <li>• <strong>Users:</strong> Website visitors</li>
            <li>• <strong>Customers:</strong> Those using IQ WORLD's services to operate digital signage</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Information We Collect</h3>
        
        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">a) Personal Information</h4>
        <p class="mb-4">When using the platform, users and customers may provide personal identifiable information (PII) such as:</p>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>• Name</li>
          <li>• Phone number</li>
          <li>• Email address</li>
          <li>• Location</li>
        </ul>

        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">b) Customer Content via Portal</h4>
        <p class="mb-4">Customers may upload content including:</p>
        <ul class="mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>• Images, videos, documents</li>
          <li>• Social media handles (Instagram, Twitter, Facebook, YouTube)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-6">
          This content is managed by the customer. IQ WORLD will only access it with explicit permission, 
          for support, debugging, or maintenance purposes. No content is sold or shared with third parties.
        </p>

        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">c) Automatic Data (Cookies)</h4>
        <p class="mb-4">IQ WORLD may collect browser and usage data such as:</p>
        <ul class="mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>• IP address</li>
          <li>• Browser type</li>
          <li>• Referring page</li>
          <li>• Search queries</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-4">Cookies may be used:</p>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>• <strong>Session cookies:</strong> To enable platform features and improve navigation</li>
          <li>• <strong>Persistent cookies:</strong> To store login information for convenience</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-6">
          You can disable cookies via your browser settings, though this may affect your experience on the platform.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h3>
        
        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">For Users:</h4>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>• Improve and operate the platform</li>
          <li>• Personalize and manage user experience</li>
          <li>• Send relevant updates or promotional material (opt-out available)</li>
        </ul>

        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">For Customers:</h4>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>• Deliver and improve platform services</li>
          <li>• Schedule and display content on digital signage</li>
          <li>• Store uploaded content securely and allow deletion by customer</li>
          <li>• Provide support, debugging, and performance tracking</li>
          <li>• Analyze usage trends and behavior</li>
          <li>• Ensure platform functionality and reliability</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">How We Share Information</h3>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-3">
          <li>• <strong>Your Account:</strong> You may review and update your account information at any time</li>
          <li>• <strong>Third-party Services:</strong> IQ WORLD may engage third-party providers for hosting, analytics, payment processing, and technical support. They are bound to use your data only for these purposes</li>
          <li>• <strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> Information may be disclosed to law enforcement or regulatory bodies if required by law or to protect IQ WORLD's rights and safety</li>
          <li>• <strong>Mergers or Acquisitions:</strong> In case of corporate restructuring, data may be transferred accordingly</li>
          <li>• <strong>Analytics:</strong> Google Analytics and similar tools may be used to understand platform behavior, governed by their privacy policies</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Managing Your Data</h3>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>• You can update or delete your profile and linked social media data at any time</li>
          <li>• Deleted social media data will be removed permanently from IQ WORLD's systems</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Security</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">IQ WORLD takes reasonable measures to protect your data against unauthorized access. However:</p>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>• IQ WORLD uses third-party hosting and infrastructure providers</li>
          <li>• While IQ WORLD owns the platform code and databases, you retain full rights over your data and may delete it anytime</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Software Limitations & Warranty Disclaimer</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">Customers must comply with software limitations. You may not:</p>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>• Circumvent technical restrictions</li>
          <li>• Reverse engineer or disassemble the software</li>
          <li>• Make unauthorized copies</li>
          <li>• Publish the software for duplication</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p class="mb-4">No warranty applies if issues result from:</p>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>• Unauthorized modifications or misuse</li>
          <li>• External viruses, malware, or Trojans</li>
          <li>• Violating usage terms</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-6 mb-8">
          <p class="text-yellow-700">
            Products outside warranty may incur additional charges.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg mt-8">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Questions or Concerns?</h4>
          <p>
            If you have any questions regarding this policy or your data, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:sales@cansignage.com" class="text-blue-600 underline">sales@cansignage.com</a><br>
            <strong>Phone:</strong> +91 91523 98498
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>